Text: I just can't get this working, the plugin shows up in ID but it doesn't open any Q files. Also it doesn't ask for any registration or password. I made absolutely sure it is in Filters>Plug-Ins. Any ideas what might be wrong?

1 got to http://www.markzware.com/downloads/files/Q2ID_updater_mac_4.zip and install the updater as described in the text file.

2 Get the latest serial box http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/5564485/Serial_Box_05-2010_Mac_OSX_%5BSerials_-_Numeros_de_serie_-_Mac%5D

4 put the activation code for Q2ID 4.17
